Class TutorDBConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.eiko.back.connect.Connector
      • com.eiko.back.connect.TutorDBConnector

  • public class TutorDBConnector
extends Connector
    This merely adds some convenience to Connector. Inserts default values for the driver, database and user. Also initializes a few queries and stores them for later use.
